Lynn Lazaroff declined to comment Wednesday on the lawsuit, saying
they hadn't received a copy of it.
   The lawsuit states that Otter has been cleared by San Bernardino
courts of his ex-wife's allegation that he sexually abused their
daughter, Leving said.
   Leving said Ms. Curtis and her daughter appeared on the
``Geraldo'' show broadcast July 18, during which Ms. Curtis
repeated her allegations.
