<DATELINE>NEW YORK (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Actress Stephanie Zimbalist isn't sure she likes
the trappings of fame. One thing is sure _ she doesn't miss
co-starring in ``Remington Steele.''
   ``Believe me, I'm very grateful to `Remington,''' the
31-year-old actress said in an interview in the latest issue of US
