<HEAD>Actress Jane Fonda Tumbles From Bicycle, Breaks Nose</HEAD>
<DATELINE>LOS ANGELES (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   Actress Jane Fonda fell off a bicycle while
pedaling down a Toronto street, smacking her head on the pavement
