   We sent up a good bill on clean water, a sound bill on clean
water, but the only way you can express your love for clean water
is to double the appropriations for clean water and then rant
against the deficit. I am for clean water. I've been an outdoorsman
and a sportsman all my life. I've been to these national parks. I
