No thanks to you -- no thanks to you. And we've been cleaning it up
for four years --
   Moderator: Governor --
   Dukakis: -- we passed landmark legislation in '84. No thanks to
you. Did everything you could to kill the Clean Water Act and the
those grants --
   Moderator: Governor --
   Dukakis: -- which make it possible for states and local
communities to clean up rivers and harbors and streams.
